\par The LD50 for skin absorption in rabbits is >2000 mg/kg.
\par 
\par }{\b\f2\fs20\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid9855598 Inhalation}{\f2\fs20\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid9855598 
